  },
  {
    question: "Can you accommodate same-day cleaning requests for last-minute bookings?",
    answer: "Yes! We understand vacation rentals operate on tight schedules. We offer same-day service when available (call before noon) and can often accommodate last-minute guest turnovers. We're flexible, responsive, and understand the importance of keeping your rental calendar full without worrying about cleaning logistics."
  },
  {
    question: "How do you handle key access for waterfront properties?",
